==English==
===Noun===
'''box-office bomb''' (''plural'' '''box-office bombs''') {{idiom}}

#A [[motion picture]] that generates relatively low [[revenue]] at the [[box office]], especially that which is less the budget for the motion picture.
#:''My favorite movie was a giant '''box office bomb.'''''

